{"tid":986113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"史上最巨！6公尺大白鯊現身夏威夷　大嗑鯨魚屍體","createTime":"2019-01-18T07:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T07:25:23.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8879a71cb5ae77f41108363c7424901410008640","tid":986113,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:47:47.000Z","msg":"大白鯊真的出現了！多年前《大白鯊》這部電影可說是轟動全球，2015年有生態紀錄片導演拍攝到身長約6公尺的巨大鯊魚「深藍」（Deep Blue），牠可以說是史上最大的鯊魚紀錄保持者。而近日有一群潛水客又意外發現了同樣巨大的伙伴！<br />\n <br />\n潛水客蘭姆西近日和朋友們在夏威夷的歐胡島進行潛水活動，沒想到竟然在外海遇到了這隻巨大的鯊魚！這隻鯊魚目測起來約6公尺長，重約2.5公噸，巨大的身軀特別寬厚，因此他們推測，牠應該是一隻懷孕的母鯊魚。<br />\n <br />\n這個奇特又美麗的同伴和蘭姆西一群人玩了一整天，他說：「我們先看到幾隻虎鯊，然後牠就出現了！所有鯊魚都閃開，而牠開始摩擦我們的船隻。」<br />\n <br />\n當時，大白鯊和其他鯊魚夥伴分食完一頭腐爛的抹香鯨屍體，吃飽飯後，牠便悠悠哉哉的往船身靠近，輕輕磨蹭船隻「抓癢癢」。<br />\n <br />\n蘭姆西表示：「她是如此龐大美麗又溫柔的巨物，她只想把我們的船隻當作抓癢工具。我們日出就出海，所以她可以說是一整天都陪著我們。」<br />\n <br />\n因為沒有進行更進一步的的研究，因此蘭姆西一群人並沒有辦法確定這隻大白鯊是否就是「深藍」，但他們一行人表示，無論是什麼樣的鯊魚，我們都應該更加愛護牠們，興奮之餘，同時也呼籲大家對於鯊魚的以及海洋環境的保護。"},{"pid":"6fae3ff7cc74161cf41e35afff58101b5d412279","tid":986113,"uid":38172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:52:06.000Z","msg":"圖?"},{"pid":"8e8977ccb707e1c0ffb15effda373f3161bde29d","tid":986113,"uid":99700,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"6fae3ff7cc74161cf41e35afff58101b5d412279","tid":986113,"uid":38172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:52:06.000Z","msg":"圖?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:55:31.000Z","msg":"太大 影唔到"},{"pid":"e9520614c45802bdd5f8392520734396f295762b","tid":986113,"uid":45781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e8977ccb707e1c0ffb15effda373f3161bde29d","tid":986113,"uid":99700,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"6fae3ff7cc74161cf41e35afff58101b5d412279","tid":986113,"uid":38172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:52:06.000Z","msg":"圖?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:55:31.000Z","msg":"太大 影唔到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:57:32.000Z","msg":"咁同條魚做愛個仔公係咪suppose 更大隻先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"45da7bfa0727c828a003d6f291892d2ff7021fdf","tid":986113,"uid":146435,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:59:06.000Z","msg":"人類對深海既知識仲差過對外太空"},{"pid":"6483d23579324b407700e60861d236b0b480b315","tid":986113,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:00:24.000Z","msg":"居然無圖"},{"pid":"c67fa81153ee1f3d7197b6940418a12a9848f524","tid":986113,"uid":4811,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:32:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xb-Ngb_Dikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fxb-Ngb_Dikw&d=099CS1sxW8vPw7uDUphh7Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=0af44cdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xb-Ngb_Dikw</a>"},{"pid":"a739ef7c2c26b6b34446ead2978745428d17bf56","tid":986113,"uid":54824,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:46:48.000Z","msg":"冇圖，冇 source<br />\n<br />\ncontent farm 文章"},{"pid":"085158b33844d5ff0c7cdfaa5e2219fe8a7ea448","tid":986113,"uid":28743,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"無圖你話自己條撚六公尺都得啦"},{"pid":"ae7e11be85ac278fe4c2a85e36eb64ee8c7734c0","tid":986113,"uid":22138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:34:32.000Z","msg":"朝早Bookmark咗諗住會有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba03769031286ae652497bac5b480508ffa6476","tid":986113,"uid":120972,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T13:39:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XqZsoesa55w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXqZsoesa55w&d=099CS1sxW8vPw7uDUphh7Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2ab9f787\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XqZsoesa55w</a>"},{"pid":"88147a205a2680a6d9ccf200f074fbfb9aa2cd71","tid":986113,"ui